\f0\b \cf0 {\listtext	1.	}Accessing PA 211
\f1\b0 \
{\listtext	2.	}Residents can call 2-1-1, text their ZIP code to 898-211, or visit www.pa211.org for web chat or localized resource listings. Services are available 24/7.\
